            <div class="warp-equation">
                <div class="result-title">WARP SPEED FORMULA</div>
                <p>For warp factors ≤ 9: v = w<sup>3</sup> × c</p>
                <p>Where:</p>
                <p>v = velocity</p>
                <p>w = warp factor</p>
                <p>c = speed of light (670,616,629 mph)</p>
            </div>
